      "date": "2012-03-14 22:57:30.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nI think this won't work in full-scale testing, since we want this test to pass in autotest when doing interop testing (i.e. when the check will fail).  Probably Yu Jian can correct me on this.",
